{"tid":83685,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"深田恭子新劇《下剋上受驗》出演老母感嘆年華老去","createTime":"2017-01-17T02:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T00:37:40.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f05d24560b6fe846caad1fdea4aa662f5d6dce27","tid":83685,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T02:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170117/large/17ee15p20e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170117%2Flarge%2F17ee15p20e.jpg&h=78316422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新一季日劇陸續開播，34歲女星深田恭子新劇《下剋上受驗》首播錄得10.9%收視，劇中她演媽媽角色，與丈夫阿部貞夫努力助囡囡考入心儀中學。深田恭子受訪時談到首度演媽媽，指劇集令她重新思考自己的年齡：「原來我已經到了可以有這麼大個女兒的年紀。」至於結婚，她則表示「沒想過」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170117/large/1484609858_01a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170117%2Flarge%2F1484609858_01a6.jpg&h=7b713247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n木村拓哉主演的TBS新劇《A LIFE~深愛的人~》前晚首播，是木村自SMAP解散後首部劇集，亦是首次挑戰醫生角色，更獲竹內結子、菜菜緒、松山研一、淺野忠信等助陣。該集收視錄得14.2%成績，荷蘭名師雲高爾宣佈退休雖撼贏昔日隊友草彅剛新劇《謊言的戰爭》（11.8%），但網民認為劇集有這個陣容，成績不算合格，同時亦創下木村開播收視最差的紀錄。"},{"pid":"aa6835309427b2d057940ad0749321c1abbb6d64","tid":83685,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T02:54:51.000Z","msg":"公子真係好鬼正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c426053dae6698c79fb00fec7b8c32736a1c052","tid":83685,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:04:25.000Z","msg":"整容雞"},{"pid":"5da5f1613a1eb399f97e94475e90688bfa567eef","tid":83685,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170117/large/17ee15p20e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F